page.title: 18LIFESTYLES IN WIS. GREEN 1
page.content: I usually get up at about six-thirty on both weekdays and weekends. Once I am awake I go and wash. Then I read for about ten minutes. After that I dress and go for a quick jog. When I get home I play on our computer until Mum gets up. For breakfast on Saturdays I just have some cereal and coffee. After breakfast I sometimes have a friend over to play. I often go down to the woods and play in the mud. When I get home it is usually time for lunch at one o'clock. On Saturdays we have bacon, eggs, tomatoes, salad and mango. This is one of my favourite lunches. After lunch I play on the computer which is a Spectrum. I have lots of games such "Starion" and "Wizard's Lair".
